{
  "stem": "7739.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I started to cry in front of him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I says, look, we were working-- we were working here before.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the last time when you worked here, a lady who was a friend of ours, went by and they gave a couple of shirts to be laundered, and I have them with me.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He searched me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I says-- he saw two white shirts, like I haven't seen white like this for a long time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anyway, he gave me a good beating and let me go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He could have shot me there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Then I went back to camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] We were there until July, I think it was, was in the summer time of 1944, where we started to dismantle the machines in the factory.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We heard that the war wasn't go so-- going so good for the Germans anymore.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they dismantled the big machines in the factory, and we loaded them on the trains.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we were in camp and not going to work anymore.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, of course, as time went by, we used to hear rumors that they were taking the people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Instead of taking them to the Ukraine, that they were being taken and gassed and burned.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, of course, nobody believed it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Or, I would say, the people that I knew didn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, why would they take healthy people that would work for them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't fight against them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't do any sabotage.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't break any laws.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Why would they take people [INAUDIBLE] gas and burn them?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] But I guess some people [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] believed.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
